Description:
In the northern temple there is a large Naga mural on the wall, you can't understand what it says but it seems to have something to do with lightning or storms.

In the centre of the mural there is a large rune that glows and overflows with energy, so it is likely that if you decipher the mural it will be activated.

There doesn't seem to be any Naga around.
DescriptionAction: Will you try to decypher the runes?
